Data

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • Data.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class implements the Item entity with the attributes id, name, type, price, description, removed. This class represents an Item. This entity class is Serializable. Allowing this entity to be written as an object into a text file.
    Since:
    24th October 2014
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Seshadri Madhavan
